      <h3>Arcadia</h3>
      <h5>
        <p>Arcadia is a health care consulting company specializing in EHR data aggregation and advanced analytics.</p>
        <p>I spent time here as a SQL Data Analyst and made queries that spanned across various databases. Technologies used here were T-SQL, P/L-SQL, and Informatica Cloud Software.</p>
        <p>Some sample queries I created used joins to link tables together. Queries would filter for certain results sucuh as NULL patient ID's, or “Test Accounts” by using wildcard characters. Informatica Cloud Agents were used to transfer data over. These lightweight clients would create secure SSH tunnels and transfer encrypted data locked with public and private keys.</p>
